name: Two-duo
tagline: A Responsive To Do Web Application
body:
### Welcome to Two Duo.
This application was designed as a sort of lorem ipsum to showcase a project portfolio in many different styles.
The application itself was written in Javascript, and was developed just to put a personal take on a traditional first time program.

### Project Locations
Two Duo project pages can be seen on github.com/TODO: add URLS

### Frameworks Used
I attempted to showcase this project using some of the most popular frameworks of today, these are: 
Twitter's Bootstrap, Zurb Foundation, and Google's Material Design Lite.
